sess potential issues involving the naming conventions of nested classes. The generated class may end up in the cglib.cglib_nodep package, which is worth noting.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_aGdzOnO4g5Gpfctwm29cucfy|fc_07b9c9d91f1d08da0169ef6b2d9f40819790083adce8127181", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "git status --short && git log --oneline -3", "timeout": 20}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1618, "output": 691, "cacheRead": 20480, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 22789, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777298207948, "responseId": "resp_07b9c9d91f1d08da0169ef6b20780c8197bb107eba1804e700"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_aGdzOnO4g5Gpfctwm29cucfy|fc_07b9c9d91f1d08da0169ef6b2d9f40819790083adce8127181", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "0b905683a7 (HEAD -> ai/add-lib-support-cglib-cglib-nodep-2.2.2) Add BeanGenerator coverage for cglib-nodep\nf7f42dc585 Cover cglib BeanCopier generator creation\n7a14357d88 Exercise cglib BeanCopier generator initialization\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777298222006}]}
